<p>Parkdale has a selection of condos and townhouses, with prices ranging from about $350 000 to around $600 000. Residential attached and detached homes are widely available in the community, going for somewhere in the vicinity of $400 000 to the high $800 000's, with more luxury homes and new infills&nbsp;in the million dollar and up range. Select your price range and/or specific Parkdale real estate below.</p>
